  "text": "14 The latter finding, combined with substantial preclinical evidence relating the RAAD effect of ketamine to its ability to induce an acute glutamate surge, [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] raised the question whether ketamine produces an acute PFC GBCr surge in MDD patients.",
  "correct_citation": {
